<li id="cite_note-tv100-99"><b><a href="#cite_ref-tv100_99-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/tv/100/list/list.php" class="external text" title="http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/tv/100/list/list.php" rel="nofollow">"The BFI TV 100: 1-100"</a>. <a href="/wiki/British_Film_Institute" title="British Film Institute">British Film Institute</a>. 2000<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/tv/100/list/list.php" class="external free" title="http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/tv/100/list/list.php" rel="nofollow">http://www.bfi.org.uk/features/tv/100/list/list.php</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-02-23</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+BFI+TV+100%3A+1-100&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.date=2000&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BBritish+Film+Institute%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bfi.org.uk%2Ffeatures%2Ftv%2F100%2Flist%2Flist.php&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:BBC"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
